++ ============================== SCRIPTS ============================== ++
+ Scripts handle complex logic that cannot be expressed declaratively.
+ They are implemented in src/story/scripts.ts and registered by index.tsx.

[script name="countdown" type="countdown"]
+ Pre chapter: 360-second countdown timer
duration=360
tickInterval=100
onEndStoryWhere=350501
[/script]
